description:
Welcome to Pet Shop Snacks!

Upgrade your bar, beautify it and stock up on the very best ingredients. Let your restaurant be the talk of the town!

Learn crazy recipes from the famous dog star chef! 

Deliver orders on time, but be careful not to mix them up! 

To work!
name: Pet Shop Snacks
intro: Take care of the kittens.  Become the owner of a pet cafe today!
